  Chiu7 ki5-to2 kong2 “Siong7-te3 ah, kiu5 Li2 lin5-bin2 sia3-bian2 goa2 koe3-khi3 e5 choe7. Goa2 sit8-chai7 u7 tek-choe7 Li2. Goa2 eng7 kan-kui2 e5 sim lai5 phian3 lang5, ia7 phian3 Siong7-te3. TaN kau3-chia it-chhe3 choe7 e5 kang-chiN5 long2 kau3-chhiu2 lah. Ah! Choe7 e5 kang-chiN5 chiu7-si7 Si2. TaN goa2 chai tu5 si2 i2-goa7, goa2 ka-ti7 bo5 lou7 thang thoat-li7.” Ki5-to2 kau3-chia chiu7 koh khui-siaN hau2 kau3 chheh khui3. Theng5 ho2-ku2 chiu7 koh chiap-soa3 ki5-to2. “Chu2 ah! Li2 si7 lin5-bin2 e5 Chu2, Li2 kiam2 m7 kheng2 lin5-bin2 chin2-kiu3 goa2? Goa2 na7-tioh8 siu7 teng7 si2-heng5, ThiN-pe7 Li2 kiam2 bo5 beh tai3-liam7 Chu2 e5 bin7, khoaN3 goa2 chit-tiap8 chin-sit8 e5 thong3-hoe2 lai5 kiu3 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5?” Chiu7 koh khui-siaN hau2, na2-hau2 soa3 na2 chin chhi-chham2 kiu5 kio3 kong2 “Chu2 ah! Chu2 ah! Kiu5 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2.” Khan3-hou7-hu7 che7-che7 si7 Ki-tok-tou5, in-ui7 Seng3 Iok-han7 tai7-hak8 si7 Kau3-hoe7 siat e5 tai7-hak8. Khau3-hou7-hu7 thiaN i teh hau2 teh ki5-to2, chiu7 chai i ia7 u7 thiaN to7-li2, chiu7 lai5 mng7 lai5 an-ui3 i. Kio3 i kin2-khun3, m7-thang sui7-bin5 put-chiok kho2-leng5 e7 koh hoat-jiat8. Au7-lai5 sin-the2 e7 koh phah-phaiN2. Teh kong2 chiah e5 oe7, a2-si7 i teh ki5-to2 e5 si5, ti7 peN7-sek au7-bin7 e5 thang-a2 goa7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 khia7 ti7 hia teh thau-khoaN3, thau-thiaN, i long2 m7-chai. Siu7 lang5 khou2-khng3 chiu7 an-cheng7 to2 loh8 khi3-khun3. Na7-si7 khun3 be7-khi3, chiu7 koh peh khi2 lai5, tui3 kou3-me5 lai5 sun5 peN7-pang5 e5 hou7-su7 tho2 choa2-pit. I e5 i3-su3 si7 ai3 sia2 ui5-gian5-chng7 hou7 Hui7-bi2. 
  In-ui7 kau3 chit e5 si5 i e5 sim iau2 u7 chit8 e5 chin-toa7 e5 gi5-hek8. (1) Chiu7-si7 i siuN7 Hui7-bi2 un2-tang3 si2 lah. Si2 ti7 lian5-hoe-ti5 te2. Tai7-khai3 si7 thau5-khak tian-to3 thau5-chai, chhap-jip8 ti7 lou7-kou-moai5 te2, chui2-chhim m7-bat ta, chin-che7 lom3-lom3 e5 thou5. Chu7 an2-ni bo5 khui3, kou-bo5, si7 si2 ti7 lou7-kou-moai5 e5 lom3-thou5 lai7. (2) Hui7-bi2 bo5 si2. In-ui7 i kam2-kak that bo5 kau3 goa7 toa7 e7, kek8-ke si7 tng3-lap-che7, an2-choaN2 e7 poah8 loh8 ti5. Loh8 ti5 an2-choaN2 e7 soa3 bo5 sin-si, chin-chiaN3 si7 ki5-koai3. Sou2-i2 chiu7 koat-sim beh sia2 ui5-gian5-chng7 hou7 Hui7-bi2. 
  Hou7-su7 theh8 choa2 pit lai5 hou7 i, i chiu7-sia2: “Sou2 thiaN3 e5 Hui7-bi2. Kiu5-li2 sia3-bian2 goa2 e5 choe7. Goa2 tui3-li2 chin put-chu7. Goan7-li2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 thoe3 goa2 ai-kiu5, in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng u7 chhim-chhim hoan2-hoe2 chai-choe7. Cheng5 goa2 chun5 kan-kui2 e5 sim phian3-li2, phian3 Siong7-te3. Sit8-chai7 chin kai-si2, taN chit-si5 goa2 tui3 sim-te2 chhim-chhim thong3-hoe2, hoat-sim sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou. Kiu5 I un-tian2 chin2-kiu3 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5. Goa2 ng3-bang7 e7-tit kap li2 saN-kiN3 ti7 thiN. Chong2-si7 goa2 iau2 u7 chit8-tiam2 e5 ng3-bang7, chiu7-si7 bang7 li2 kho2-leng5 iau2 ti7 se3-kan. Na7-si7 chit e5 ng3-bang7 si7 chin poh8, kiam2-chhai2 si7 goa2 e5 gong7-siuN7. Chong2-si7 goa2 i2-keng chai, goa2 e7 siu7 hoat-lut8 e5 chhai5-phoaN3. Goa2 bo5 lou7 thang ka-ti7 se2-chheng. Ah! Sou2 thiaN3--e5. Siat-su2 li2 na7 iau2-oah8, li2 kiam2 be7 tai3-liam7 tioh8 chhou-hoe7 ti7 soaN-teng2 ban2 Pek-hap8-hoe e5 si5. Kiam2 be7 siuN7 tioh8 choe3-hoe2 kou3 A-pa ti7 peN7-chhng5. Kiam2 be7 siuN7 tioh8 goa2 tui-chhoe7 li2, chhoe7 li2 ti7 Hun5-lam5-siaN5-goa7 e5 chit8 e5 hiuN-chng e5 sio2-tek-ui5 e5 cheng5-keng2. Ah! Na7 koh siuN7 hiah e5 tiN-bit8 e5 ai3-cheng5, goa2 e5 sim sit8-chai7 beh piak-lih8.” Sia2 kau3 chia bak8-sai2 hou3 m7-khui tit8-tit8 hau2 chhut--lai5, chiu7 khi2-lai5 kiaN5-oa2 au7-piah thang-a2-kiN beh theh8 bin7-kin chhit bak8-sai2. Hut-jian5 taN-thau5 khoaN3 thang-a2-goa7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5, hit e5 lang5-iaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 Hui7-bi2! I bo5 i3-sek kio3 chin toa7-siaN “Hui7-bi2”! Chong2-si7 hit e5 lang5-iaN2 chu7 an2-ni bo5 khi3. I chin m7-goan7 chu7 chheng7 khun3-saN khui-mng5 jiok chhut--lai5. Ko2-jian5 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 teh chau2, ji5-chhiaN2 si7 cha-bou2-lang5 e5 khoan2. In-ui7 goeh8 bo5 kng, tak tioh8 chioh8-thau5 soa3 phak-loh8-khi3, khi2 nau2 pin5-hiat, kou3 me5 e5 hou7-su7 kin2-lai5, ia7 kap hit e5 teh chau2 e5 lang5 ia7 oat to3-tng2--lai5. Ka7 i kng jip8 peN7-pang5. Theng5 oa2 chiaN5-khek ku2 chia cheng-sin5. Sim chin giau5-gi5, s