  Kau3 chit8-le2-pai3 au7 chiu7 koh siu7 tiau3 kau3 hoat-iN7 siu7 u5-sim2. U5-sim2 koaN tai7-seng mng7 i e5 seN3-mia5, ni5-hoe3, chu7-chi2. Khak-jin7 chit-e5 lang5 ko2-jian5 si7 Tan5 Khun-hong, Tan5 Hok-choan5 si7 ke2-mia5, it-it chu7-jin7. Ia7 ka-ti7 chu7-jin7 si7 ui7 kiaN choe7, sou2-i2 chiah to5-choe7 lai5 Siong7-hai2. Thang-kong2 10 hun e5 8, 9 i ka-ti7 seng5-jin7 Hui7-bi2 e5 si2 si7 i ka7 i that loh8 khi3 e5. Put-ko3 u7 kui2-na7 tiam2 thang koh tiau-cha chiu7-si7. (1) Si7 ok-i3, a2-si7 bu5-i3. (2) Si7 i chit8 e5 ka7 i that lai5 ti3-si2, a2-si7 iau2 u7 pang-chhiu2. Na7 siat-su2 u7 pang-chhiu2, chiu7 piN3-choe3 ok-i3, kiong7-bou5. (3) ChaiN2-iuN7 e7 biat8-si. An2-ni si7 poah8 loh8-chui2 si2, a2-si7 ti7 pat8-ui7 i2-keng ka7 i chhong3-si2, chiah kng lai5 thiam ti7 Lian5-hoe-ti5, ke2 choe3 poah8-loh8-chui2 si2. In-ui7 si7 biat8-si, sou2-i2 lang5 poah8-loh8-chui2 ka-ti7 kou-bo5, ia7 bo5 lang5 lai5 po3 keng2-chhat. Tui3 chit 3 tiam2 iau2 boe7 beng5. 
  Ui7 beh phoaN3-koat si2-heng5 tek-khak ai3 u7 jin5-cheng3 , but8-cheng3 , khong-kan, si5-kan, tong7-chok it-chhe3 iu2-lek8 e5 cheng3-ku3, m7-si7 sui5-sui5 pian7-pian7, chiu7 koat-teng7 chiong chit kiaN7 an3 i5 to3-khi3 pun2 te7-hng e5 Te7-hng-hoat-iN7. Soa3 thang sit8-te7 kiam2-cheng3. Keh jit8 chiu7 lian5-jin5 tai3-an3, ah-sang3 loh8 lai5 Chiang-chiu-siaN5 Te7-hng hoat-iN7. Chit-khi2 an3 Keng2-bu7-chhu3 phoe hou7 Chhoa3 Thian-peng5 sian-siN choan-an3 cheng-cha. Sou2-i2 Chhoa3 sian-siN chhin-sin ah i loh8-lai5 Chiang-chiu. Kau3-chia Khun-hong chin-chiaN3 si7 bo5 bin7 thang kiN3 lang5. Loh8 hoe2-chhia khoaN3-kiN3 e5 lang5 u7 e5 bih-chhui3, u7 e5 phui3-noa7. Tai7-ke kong2 i si7 liau2-boe2-a2-kiaN2, hong-im5 chiu2-sek bo5 theng5-tou7. Kau3-ui7 keh-jit8 kap chin-che7 hoat-keng2, hoat-i , Chhoa3 Sian-siN chhin-sin khan, thau5-khak ka7 i ti3 chhau2-lap-a2, kan-ta chhun bak8-chiu khang hou7 i khoaN3-lou7, chhiu2, khau3 chhiu2-khau3 pak8 iap-au7. Khan lai5 kau3 Lian5-hoe-ti5 piN, jin5-san, jin5-hai2 e5 lang5 ui5 lai5 khoaN3. Sit8-chai7 chiok kian3-siau3. Kio3 i ka-ti7 siong7-se3 soat-beng5, Hui7-bi2 ti7 to2-ui7 lam2 li2 e5 kha, lin2 saN e5 an2-choaN2 moa? Lam2-kha lam2 sim2-mih8 se3-bin7? Lam2-kha chu7 an2-ni theng5 kha khia7 leh, a2-si7 u7 lam2 teh kiaN5? KiaN5 kui2-pou7? M7-chai iaN2 kau3 ti5-piN lah a2 m7-si7? That goa7 toa7 e7, pi2 khoaN3-mai7? That chit8-e7 sui5-si5 poah8 loh8 khi3, a2-si7 theng5 chit8 e7-a2 chiah poah8 loh8 khi3? Bo5 sui5-si5 in3-siaN poah8-loh8 khi3, si7 iau2 u7 lang5 tau3 that loh8 khi3 a2 m7-si7? Kau3-chia chit-ku3 i siuN7 chin ku2 be7-hiau2 in3, Kak-tit m7-si7 i that-khi3 chek-si5 poah8 loh8-khi3. Na2-chun2 u7 …, m7-ku2 am3-am3, ka-ti7 u7 lim-chiu2 sio2-khoa2 chui3-chui3, sou2-i2 ki3-ek put-chheng-chho2 m7-kaN2 in3. Li2 u7 hoah kiu3 lang5 a2-bo5? U7. Li2 u7 loh8 khi3 kou a2-bo5? Goa2 chek-si5 loh8 khi3 hoe5. U7 thng3-e5 a2-bo5? Bo5 thng3-e5, kan-ta ti7 hoaN7-teng2 aN3 loh8 khi3 bong. An2-choaN2 koan-he7 jin5-beng7 hiah lo2-chho2, m7-bian2 thng3 e5, kin2 giah8 hoe2 lai5 bong? Siu3-chhun kio3 goa2 mai3, kong2 chin-koaN5, goa2 u7 lim-chiu2, ia7 sio2-khoa2 kam2-tioh8. Kong2 si2 to si2 lah, bin5-a2-chai3 chiah lai5 kou. Au7-lai5 chu7 an2-ni tan2 kau3 bin5-a2-chai3 a2 m7-si7? M7-si7, goa2 u7 giah8 tek-ko lai5 la7. Hit-si5 Siu3-chhun ti7 to2-ui7? I m7-chhap goa2 choe3 i to2-teh khun3. 
  Chhoa3 sian-siN te7 6 kam2 si7 kam2-kak Siu3-chhun tui3 chit-chan5 su7 ia7-si7 chit8 e5 Chu2-kak, chek-si5 kio3 chit8 e5 heng5-keng2 khi3 kio3 Siu3-chhun lai5. Kio3 i lai5 Lian5-hoe-ti5-piN kiam2-cheng3. Heng5-keng2 khi3 e5 si5 chhoe7 bo5. To3-tng2 lai5 po3-ko3, kong2 lai7-bin7 chhoe7 bo5 lang5, pang5-keng chi2 u7 chit8 e5 eN-a2 teh-hau2, chin ki5-koai3, it-hoat kho2-gi5 chit e5 lang5 u7 choe7-hiam5. Sou2-i2 beng7-leng7 choan5-chhu3-theh8 lai7-goa7 chong2 sou-cha. Tauh ti2 Siu3-chhun tui3 to2-ui7 khi3? Kau3-boe2 chiah hoat-kian3 i si2 ti7 au7 hoe-hng5 e5 kou2-chiN2-te2. In-ui7 lang5 thoa Khun-hong beh lai5 kiam2-cheng3 e5 si5, i iaN2 tioh8 Khun-hong bin7 ti3 chhau2-lap-a2, chhiu2 hou7 lang5 pak8 iap-au7, eng7 chhiu2-khau3 khau3 leh. Siu3-chhun toa7-kiaN, chai si2 lah. Koh-si7 choan5-kok ti-mia5 e5 Chhoa3 cheng-tham3 choan-an3 cheng-pan7. Chai hoat-bong2 lan5-to5. I ka-ti7 chai, chha5 kau3-boe2 chu2-hoan7 m7-si7 Khun-hong. Chu2-hoan7 si7 i pun2-sin, Khun-hong si7 bu5-i3, na7-si7 iu2-i3 chun5 sat-jin5, koh tit8-chiap e5 ti3-si2 si7 tui3 i e5 heng5-tong7. Sou2-i2 kau3-chia i siuN7 khi2 hoat-teng5 hian7-si3, m7-tat8-tioh8 si2 tiam3 chhu3-nih khah tit8. Sou2-i2 chiong Eng5-chong(eN-a2) ka7 i hiat tiam3 bin5-chhng5, than3 lang5 bo5 chu3-i3 chu7 an2-ni khi3 thiau3 kou2-chiN2. I m7-si7 eng7 thiau3, i si7 eng7 tian-to3-thau5-chai chai loh8 khi3. Sou2-i2 kou khi2--lai5 i2-keng koe3-khui3 nge7-nge7, si5-kan ia7 i2-keng koe3 30 hun khah ke. Thau5-khak chai ti7 chiN2-te2 e5 lou5-kou-moai5, sou2-i2 chit8 chhui3 chit8 phiN7, si3-ke3 long2 si7 lou5-kou-moai5 that tiN7-tiN7. Tui3 u7 chui2-to7, chit e5 cheN2 han2 tit eng7 chin chhim, chui2 ia7 u7 chhau3-bi7, kau3-boe2 kiu3 be7 oah8. Na7-si7 tong5-si5 sou-cha, ti7 Hui7-bi2 e5 pang5-keng u7 hoat-kian3 tioh8 Hui7-bi2 chu7-sat e5 ui5-gian5-chng7, che-si7 chin ki5-koai3 e5 su7. 
  An2-ni chit e5 an3 chin tiN5. Ho2 e5 cheng3-jin5 Bi2-chu ti7 Siong7-hai2 Te7-it li2-sia7 hou7 lang5 thau7-si2. U7 chu2-hoan7 a2-si7 tong5-bou7-hoan7 kho2-gi5 e5 Siu3-chhun ui3-choe7 chu7-sat. I5-it e5 but8-cheng3 si7 nng7-tiau5 e5 chhiu2-kin. Chit8-tiau5 Hui7-bi2 e5. Chit8-tiau5 Siu3-chhun e5 long2 i2-keng chai. Choe3 hiam5-gi5 e5 Siu3-chhun ki3-jian5 be5 tit chhut-teng5. Sou2-i2 taN chi2-u7 sim2-phoaN3 Khun-hong. Koat-teng7 lai5 12 goeh8 14 jit8 beh ti7 Chiang-chiu siaN5 Te7-hng hoat-iN7 kong-phoaN3. Hit-jit8 8 tiam2 beh khui-teng5. Koe3-khi3 si7 chit8 e5 te7-hng e5 beng5-bong7-ka, koh sin-bun5 chhut chiah toa7 ji7, koh chit8-si5 saN e5 bou2, chiah hia-pai. Hut-jian5 3 e5 bou2 ui7 i chit8 e5 choe3 tiong-sim long2 si2. Ji5-chhiaN2 si2 tit chin li7-ki5. Toa7-bou2 siu7 that loh8-ti5 si2, te7-ji7-ho7 i5-thai3-thai3 hou7 lang5 thau7-si2, te7-it-ho7 i5-thai3-thai3 thiau3 kou2-cheN2 si2. Long2 si2 ti7 hui-beng7, an2-ni se3-siok8 lang5 long2 kong2 chit8 e5 Khun-hong tek-khak e7 hou7 cha-bou2-kui2 kau-tiN5 lai5 liah8-khi3. Oan-hun5 tek-khak m7-soaN3, e7 lai5 kau-tiN5. Kong-phoaN3 hit-jit8 chiok-che7 lang5, tioh8 theh8 pai5-a2-ho7 chiah e7 tit jip8 khi3. 
